OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FThe 7am weekday train from Manchester
OL,7,FPiccadilly to London Euston will run
OL,8,Fwithout any passengers on board
OL,9,Ffollowing a ruling by the rail
OL,10,Fregulator.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Office of Rail
OL,13,Fand Road (ORR), the independent safety
OL,14,Fand economic regulator for Britain's
OL,15,Frailways, said continuing the Avanti
OL,16,Fservice on the West Coast Main Line
OL,17,Fwould "harm the overall performance
OL,18,Ffor all passengers".
