OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FFrom December 15, the 7am service -
OL,7,Fnicknamed the "ghost train" - will run
OL,8,Fwith only staff on board so that it
OL,9,Fcan be easily moved or delayed to
OL,10,Falleviate pressure on what is a
OL,11,F"congested stretch of track", the ORR
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe early-morning commuter service has
OL,15,Fbeen running successfully up until
OL,16,Fnow, so what has changed?
