OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FA new rail operator - Lumo - will
OL,7,Fbegin offering services on the West
OL,8,FCoast Main Line from December. The all-
OL,9,Felectric trains have been running on
OL,10,Fthe east coast between London and
OL,11,FEdinburgh since 2021.
OL,13,FLumo is an open-access operator, which
OL,14,Fmeans it is an independent company
OL,15,Fthat runs train services on a railway
OL,16,Fnetwork without a government franchise
OL,17,Fagreement and receives no government
OL,18,Fsubsidies.
