OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FIt has received permission from the
OL,7,FORR to run services from Stirling to
OL,8,FLondon Euston starting in December,
OL,9,Fwhich will add to congestion on the
OL,10,Fline.
OL,12,FAvanti was only given the rights to
OL,13,Frun the 7am Manchester to London
OL,14,FEuston service for one timetable
OL,15,Fperiod - from May to December 2025.
OL,17,FAn ORR spokesperson explained that to
OL,18,Fcontinue running that service, those
OL,19,Ftrains would have had to use what is
OL,20,Fcalled a 'firebreak path', which is
OL,21,Freserved for managing disruption.
