OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FA spokesperson explained: "If Avanti
OL,7,Fruns the train empty on this schedule,
OL,8,Fi.e. without passengers, it allows
OL,9,Fthem to maintain movements so that
OL,10,Ftheir trains are still in the right
OL,11,Fplaces for all their other services,
OL,12,Fbut if there is disruption, the train
OL,13,Fcan be moved or delayed much more
OL,14,Feasily than a scheduled passenger
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,17,F"This flexibility helps manage
OL,18,Fperformance for all passengers using
OL,19,Fthe whole West Coast Main Line and
OL,20,Frecover services during disruption
OL,21,Fmore easily."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
