OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FHow has Avanti West Coast responded?
OL,8,FAn Avanti spokesperson said the
OL,9,Fcompany was "disappointed" by the
OL,10,FORR's decision.
OL,12,FThe spokesperson added that some other
OL,13,Fservices - including a Sunday train
OL,14,Ffrom Holyhead to London, which will
OL,15,Fnow terminate at Crewe - will also be
OL,16,Fimpacted.
