OL,3,CWhy early-morning 'ghost train' will
OL,4,Crun without any passengers
OL,6,FAvanti continued: "This will clearly
OL,7,Fimpact those customers who already use
OL,8,Fthese services. However, we will still
OL,9,Fbe delivering even more services
OL,10,Facross our network from the start of
OL,11,Fthe December timetable, including
OL,12,Ffurther additional trains on our
OL,13,FLiverpool route."
OL,15,FThere will be a new timetable in May
OL,16,F2026, where Avanti hopes the 7am
OL,17,FManchester to London service will be
OL,18,Freinstated.
